text: Safet Džinović (11 March 1921 – 18 December 1997) was a Yugoslav Partisan, economist and the first president of the assembly of Bosnian football club FK Sarajevo. ==References== Category:1921 births Category:1997 deaths Category:People from Sarajevo Category:FK Sarajevo presidents of the assembly Category:Bosniaks of Bosnia and Herzegovina Category:University of Sarajevo alumni Category:Bosnia and Herzegovina economists
title: Safet Džinović
